{"Sid":0,"Did":118190,"Id":"282403","Title":"宜蘭城隍廟三川殿活動六角石","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/bb8edc5b-358f-49db-858d-442507f4d01a/collection/5dde4a5e-3b5c-4e9f-aed9-bbfddf88617a/108-her-pa-1964-201911011616275dbbd63fc2f500.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n宜蘭城隍廟三川殿內是採六角形洗石子地板，但在近三川殿中央處有一塊六角形石塊，並非固定，而是活動的，站於其上會有左右搖晃不穩定之感。為何有此活動六角石，說法甚多，莫衷一是。有一說是其性質類似城隍廟內城隍爺用以計算某人在世時做了多少善事惡事之大算盤；城隍爺亦可以此活動六角石為秤，秤量死後來城隍廟報到之人一生做了多少善事惡事。另有一說，則認為是當初城隍廟重修時的奠基石，也就是起工時的基準點。亦有認為，只是單純的清理地板下排水道的設施。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.751056","Keyword_Latitude":"24.7588978","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/63CEE6F6-FC48-4D4D-8F43-207E4DFF9AA8","Original_Identifier":"282403","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"三川殿 / 六角石 / 宜蘭城隍廟","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 15:32:29","timelines":"","place":"宜蘭縣宜蘭市城隍街12號","address":"宜蘭縣宜蘭市城隍街12號","longitude":"121.751056","latitude":"24.7588978","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"林鴻文/ 蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-24/bb8edc5b-358f-49db-858d-442507f4d01a/collectionOpen/f34b1173-8baf-44a8-9e32-357886815e62/108-her-pa-1964-re-201911011617445dbbd63fc2f500.jpg"}}